quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  6,95,Inna Allāha Fāliqu Al-Ĥabbi Wa An-Nawá Yukhriju Al-Ĥayya Mina Al-Mayyiti Wa Mukhriju Al-Mayyiti Mina Al-Ĥayyi Dhalikumu Allāhu Fa'anná Tu'ufakūna
  6,96,Fāliqu Al-'Işbāĥi Wa Ja`ala Al-Layla Sakanāan Wa Ash-Shamsa Wa Al-Qamara Ĥusbānāan Dhālika Taqdīru Al-`Azīzi Al-`Alīmi
  6,97,Wa Huwa Al-Ladhī Ja`ala Lakumu An-Nujūma Litahtadū Bihā Fī Žulumāti Al-Barri Wa Al-Baĥri Qad Faşşalnā Al-'Āyāti Liqawmin Ya`lamūna
  6,98,Wa Huwa Al-Ladhī 'Ansha'akum Min Nafsin Wāĥidatin Famustaqarrun Wa Mustawda`un Qad Faşşalnā Al-'Āyāti Liqawmin Yafqahūn
  6,99,Wa Huwa Al-Ladhī 'Anzala Mina As-Samā'i Mā'an Fa'akhrajnā Bihi Nabāta Kulli Shay'in Fa'akhrajnā Minhu Khađirāan Nukhriju Minhu Ĥabbāan Mutarākibāan Wa Mina An-Nakhli Min Ţal`ihā Qinwānun Dāniyatun Wa Jannātin Min 'A`nābin Wa Az-Zaytūna Wa Ar-Rummāna Mushtabihāan Wa Ghayra Mutashābihin Anžurū 'Ilá Thamarihi 'Idhā 'Athmara Wa Yan`ihi 'Inna Fī Dhālikum La'āyātin Liqawmin Yu'uminūna
  6,100,Wa Ja`alū Lillāhi Shurakā'a Al-Jinna Wa Khalaqahum Wa Kharaqū Lahu Banīna Wa Banātin Bighayri `Ilmin Subĥānahu Wa Ta`ālá `Ammā Yaşifūna
  6,101,Badī`u As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi 'Anná Yakūnu Lahu Waladun Wa Lam Takun Lahu Şāĥibatun Wa Khalaqa Kulla Shay'in Wa Huwa Bikulli Shay'in `Alīmun